1. Install rust:
    curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh

2. Install Protobuff:
    brew install protobuf

2. Dependencies:
    cargo add prost
    cargo add tonic 
    cargo add tokio --features macros,rt-multi-thread


4. Build Dependencies:
    cargo add tonic-build --build


5. React gRPC Client:
    1. https://daily.dev/blog/build-a-chat-app-using-grpc-and-reactjs
    2. https://www.koyeb.com/tutorials/build-and-deploy-a-grpc-web-app-using-rust-tonic-and-react